{"id": 2996, "genre": 1000, "title": "你会在哪些时刻意识到自己似乎被“效率”绑架了？", "description": "一个谜思：总觉得“生活还可以再高效一点”，结果好像反而被所谓的“优化”困住了。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 8755, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190909213157YTX6WyuOzxpHDAjv.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-11T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5903, "title": "你会在哪些时刻意识到自己似乎被“效率”绑架了？", "content": "生活中你都有哪些“效率错觉”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 346230, "content": "随时随地都要节约时间，节约下来的时间也不知道能花在哪里", "image": "img/option/option/20190909221403UXldIBQoT390YOms.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346231, "content": "忍不住尝试各种“高效学习法”，最后根本不会用", "image": "img/option/option/20190909221515tN3AnmoxScdYyJls.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346232, "content": "安装了各种效率应用（虽然可能从来没打开过", "image": "img/option/option/20190909223355ndsoVEap2UP6wYvF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346233, "content": "即使根本没必要 multitasking，也会尽量多线程", "image": "img/option/option/20190909224949k8CY9MROr2ZTLs5e.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346234, "content": "晚睡的时候总担心“不能什么都没干就这么睡了”", "image": "img/option/option/20190909224512KRFZo7vNDOq2iUC4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346235, "content": "连工作间隙的摸鱼，也想着要高效地偷懒", "image": "img/option/option/20190909222337SouymcMUOiRjI2nl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346236, "content": "去旅游去放松，也要用最少时间逛最多地方", "image": "img/option/option/20190911173250YgZ28WSh6saEVKXr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 346237, "content": "就算闲下来，也总要做点什么填满这段时间", "image": "img/option/option/20190909222249d93wCipkR0TGmQnX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}